data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the desirable East Lake Subdivision! This immaculate 4-bedroom residence offers a perfect blend of style, comfort, and functionality. The main level boasts an open floor plan, featuring a versatile office/playroom, a welcoming family room with a gas log fireplace, a formal dining room, and a well-appointed kitchen. The kitchen is a chef's delight with stainless steel appliances, granite counters, and a charming breakfast nook.    Ascending to the second level, discover the expansive master suite with a walk-in closet and a private bathroom, creating a serene retreat. Three additional bedrooms provide ample space for family or guests, and the 4th bedroom, generously sized, could serve as a bonus room for added versatility.    Step outside and experience the outdoor paradisea"enjoy the fresh air on the screened-in porch, entertain on the grilling patio, or let your pets roam freely in the fenced backyard. This home offers a perfect balance of indoor and outdoor living.    Conveniently located for a short commute to Seymour Johnson AFB, this property not only fulfills your living needs but also provides easy access to essential amenities. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home and experience the perfect blend of modern living and comfort!
